{"tid":1786190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國央行：香港政局持續緊張　50 億美元撤資","createTime":"2019-12-17T03:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T05:42:48.000Z","uid":152476,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a195b27a6dff7cfa89d4fde54f9da7e6d3ff0fdc","tid":1786190,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國中央銀行英倫銀行（Bank of England）發表金融穩定報告，指由於香港緊張政治局勢持續，自今年 4 月開始，至今累計已有約 50 億美元資金從香港的投資基金撤出，折合約 390 億港元。根據英倫銀行計算及 Refinitiv 和 EPFR Global 數據，上述數字相當於本港生產總值的 1.25%。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社又引述英資銀行滙豐控股和渣打集團指，由於本港示威活動加劇投資者憂慮，一些香港的富裕客戶決定在海外開設銀行賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/英國央行-香港政局持續緊張-50-億美元撤資/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-50-%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%92%A4%E8%B3%87%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0stNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=22196476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5-50-%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%92%A4%E8%B3%87%2F&h=d83960fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/英國央行-香港政局持續緊張-50-億美元撤資/</a>"},{"pid":"f2e999b7fd07e307e178352c208db806bf2caa18","tid":1786190,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"【第十柒期牆紙】起來，不願做奴隸的人們<br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0stNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=f5340fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t